dsDescriptionValue.value: Masks for the Giant Molecular Filaments (GMFs) used in Zucker, Battersby, & Goodman 2018 (submitted). Original characterization of the GMFs can be found in Ragan et al. 2014 and Abreu-Vicente et al. 2016. These are the same masks shown via the green contours in section 6.2.4 in the Appendix, derived by applying an integrated intensity threshold to 13CO emission maps.
